{"tid":285470,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿ 普巴新髮型 波霸冧中國","createTime":"2017-06-15T23:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T12:15:41.000Z","uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"038894cd8d235f519dbc2f439e9e5e689dd8f9b2","tid":285470,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T23:02:07.000Z","msg":"﻿普巴新髮型 波霸冧中國<br />\n2017-06-16 03:00:00<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】曼聯球星保羅普巴為迎接即將展開的中國行，特別在後腦剪了「波霸」兩漢字的髮型，並拍照上載到社交網站跟球迷分享。不過，球迷並不欣賞，卻借其世界紀錄一億零五百萬歐羅身價揶揄：「水貨一個還敢叫波霸！」<br />\n<br />\n保羅普巴於英超休季後馬不停蹄，周二才代表法國友賽英格蘭，下周一便會親臨香港參與贊助商旗艦店的開幕儀式，並有機會與小球迷接觸切磋球技。據報，他還會造訪北京、上海等地。<br />\n<br />\n為隆重其事，這名全球最高身價球員特別在出發前剪了一頭中國風格髮型，「波霸」兩字清晰可見，並在社交媒體寫上「中國，我來也」的字句。可是，網民以此髮型揶揄他：「水貨波霸！又黑又醜，換個髮型仍是醜！」<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20170616/7560606/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsoccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2F1%2F20170616%2F7560606%2F&d=rXNzXHNz84wjncQk%2Ft7N%2BwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=29f0b8f4\" target=\"_blank\">http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20170616/7560606/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/74f135fa96cfc8b907038f68724b9a26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F74f135fa96cfc8b907038f68724b9a26.jpg&h=8ead3a68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75907f786e248ff7797728d9a2a7c3d88386c19d","tid":285470,"uid":12518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T23:06:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"690f2a4be62987299f1dc1dc202adebaa4b20d66","tid":285470,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T23:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebf65702b617ec0c1bd4c9d9e8dedee24a46b53","tid":285470,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T23:07:49.000Z","msg":"唔整個柒字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12996ed4cb2d14efb210158b7508530a5ae48349",